cs.IR, cs.DL, cs.HC, cs.SI, cs.CL

The paper discusses the challenges of information retrieval and knowledge organization, which are central topics in the field of Information Retrieval (cs.IR). It also touches upon digital libraries (cs.DL) and the design of user interfaces (cs.HC) for navigating large information spaces. The paper also mentions the use of social tagging (cs.SI) and classification systems (cs.CL) for organizing knowledge. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.IR, cs.DL, cs.HC, cs.SI, and cs.CL, in that order.
